question.string: which creatures not speaking draconic language do have chaotic good alignment?
does Caypup have more special abilities than Aasimar?
how many creatures with non-neutral alignment do speak treant language?

query.sparql:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?creature) AS ?count)
WHERE {
  ?creature <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#Beast> .
  ?creature <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasAlignment> ?alignment .
  ?creature <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasLanguages> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#TreantL> .
  
  # Exclude neutral alignments by filtering out any alignment URI containing "neutral" (case-insensitive)
  FILTER (!CONTAINS(LCASE(STR(?alignment)), "neutral"))
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?robot) AS ?count)
WHERE {
  ?robot <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://example.org/Robot> .
  ?robot <http://example.org/intelligence> ?intelligence .
  ?robot <http://example.org/speed> ?speed .
  FILTER(?intelligence < 7 && ?speed > 10)
}

question.string: which creatures speaking necril and abyssal languages do have wisdom attribute more than 4?

query.sparql:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?beast WHERE {
  ?beast <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#Beast> .

  ?beast <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#wis> ?wis .

}

question.string: does Baalzebul have a greater value of average statistics than Dagon?

query.sparql:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
ASK WHERE {
  <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#DagonDemonPrinceoftheSea> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasCRValue> ?dagonCR .
  <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#DagonDemonPrinceoftheSea> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasACValue> ?dagonAC .
  <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#DagonDemonPrinceoftheSea> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasHPvalue> ?dagonHP .

  <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#Baalzebul> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasCRValue> ?baalzebulCR .
  <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#Baalzebul> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasACValue> ?baalzebulAC .
  <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#Baalzebul> <http://www.semanticweb.org/annab/ontologies/2022/3/ontology#hasHPvalue> ?baalzebulHP .

  BIND((?dagonCR + ?dagonAC + ?dagonHP) / 3 AS ?dagonAvg)
  BIND((?baalzebulCR + ?baalzebulAC + ?baalzebulHP) / 3 AS ?baalzebulAvg)

  FILTER(?baalzebulAvg > ?dagonAvg)
}
